data.description: 4.75% FHA Assumable Loan!  Call to learn details and more! Elegant 1927 Spanish bungalow,  brilliantly upgraded and restored in 2019.  This 2 bedroom 2 bath darling is flooded with beautiful natural light and features a quintessential barrel ceiling, stunning arch window, original front door, decorative fireplace, classic wooden windows, stunning wide plank floors and a modern kitchen. Primary bedroom with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet.  In house washer and dryer, one car garage and a lush landscaped retreat. Upgrades in 2020 include upgraded electric, tankless water heater, and bathrooms featuring Mohawk Revwood.Easy access to the best that Los Angeles has to offer, from cultural attractions to dining, and shopping destinations. Situated in Hyde Park neighboring Leimert Park, View Park and Windsor Hills it's near  SoFi stadium, Baldwin Hills Crenshaw Plaza and a 15-minute drive to Culver City, Playa Vista, LAX and Downtown Los Angeles.  This home is just around the corner from the 10 mile green biking and walking path connecting Slauson Station to the LA River.  Some neighborhood spots include Hilltop Coffee + Kitchen, Sip and Sonder, Harun, Jon & Vinny's, Post and Beam and the sprawling Kenneth Hahn State Recreation Area which has a new Playa Vista Trail which connects to Culver City.
